      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   qry-let-seq-000      thru qry-let-seq-999        .
           if        w-cnt-qry-flg-sub    not  = spaces
                     move   spaces        to   w-cnt-qry-flg-sub
                     go to  qry-rou-pri-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
